      "cooked": "<aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://www.reporter.al/2016/12/05/kredite-e-keqija-rritje-e-pandalshme/\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/5/7/574bfd1d6d53fc8f58c8d802b60eed5b9c76e19d.png\" class=\"site-icon\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://www.reporter.al/2016/12/05/kredite-e-keqija-rritje-e-pandalshme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"06:31PM - 05 December 2016\">Reporter.al – 5 Dec 16</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:600/371;\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/3X/a/c/ac427126d7fb29ef64f5c86edeacbc04f10f29c9.png\" class=\"thumbnail\" width=\"600\" height=\"371\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.reporter.al/2016/12/05/kredite-e-keqija-rritje-e-pandalshme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kreditë e këqija, rritje e pandalshme</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Treguesi i kredive të këqija të sistemit bankar shënoi kuotën 21.35 për qind të totalit të kredive në muajin tetor,</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n",
